{"tid":1146931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"五月九號佢同我攤牌了 好心痛 但好舒暢","createTime":"2019-05-09T14:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T19:09:17.000Z","uid":250476,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9dc14e1d96c05cf8c291f72bba8cf6df72a639","tid":1146931,"uid":250476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"應該一早明白 <br />\n錯過咗就係錯過咗  <br />\n無論你做咗幾多嘢 返唔到嚟就係返唔到嚟<br />\n應該一早要放低 <br />\n唔好再成日呃自己 <br />\n<br />\n對唔住 令到你覺得我好煩 <br />\n令到你好怕 <br />\n聽到你頭先同我講你話好怕 <br />\n我再諗返真係覺得自己好痴線<br />\n我覺得真係好對你唔住<br />\n之前應承過你嘅嘢做唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好感激遇到你<br />\n我知你喺度你會睇到<br />\n就算我同你講過幾多次 <br />\n我都想同你講多一次<br />\n係你令我識得愛一個人 對一個人好 <br />\n就算以前比人話成舊木咁唔識氹人<br />\n係你令到我由唔識氹人<br />\n慢慢開始每次同你講電話都同你傾得好開心成日聽到你笑 哩樣係我覺得同你最值得記念嘅一樣嘢 <br />\n呢樣嘢永遠都會喺我心裏面"},{"pid":"10aed92ecfaba80a35bd8cfc835ede0a9ec6f9b6","tid":1146931,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"咩事？"},{"pid":"f6770932bb87db39d9b2f61371edd588d5d7c068","tid":1146931,"uid":250476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10aed92ecfaba80a35bd8cfc835ede0a9ec6f9b6","tid":1146931,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算叫分手嘅分手"},{"pid":"a0fb743d8f02a23a06dcde95fb58c8d1bf23f2df","tid":1146931,"uid":250476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"開始要習慣咗無佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e61755a01f26b6e2d6c9b1b1271a93428e62539","tid":1146931,"uid":87781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0fb743d8f02a23a06dcde95fb58c8d1bf23f2df","tid":1146931,"uid":250476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"開始要習慣咗無佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets